list.abstract: 《Already》是由歌手Not yet演唱的一首日语歌曲，于2014年4月23日发行，收录于专辑《already》中。

yingyinNormal.en: But he had already moved on. Already? that was quick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但他已经有新欢了。已经？好快啊。

yingyinNormal.en: And what if they already know? Then you're already dead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果他们已经知道了呢？那你死定了。

yingyinNormal.en: You already did. To Emily.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你已经做了，对艾米莉。

yingyinNormal.en: I've already put together my team.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我已经组织了团队。

yingyinNormal.en: Or have you already scented blood?
yingyinNormal.zh: 还是你已经起了杀心了？

yingyinNormal.en: But you already told me everything.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可是你都已经告诉我了。

yingyinNormal.en: My goodness, five o'clock already.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的天啊，已经五点钟了。

yingyinNormal.en: My goodness, five o'clock already.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的天啊，已经五点钟了。

yingyinNormal.en: But, they already think he's dead.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是，他们已经以为他死了。

yingyinNormal.en: I can't believe Emma's already 1.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真不敢相信，爱玛已经一岁了。

yingyinNormal.en: Nothing. I've already told my side.
yingyinNormal.zh: 没什么，我能说的已经说了。

yingyinNormal.en: Regular Celery. Oh, I already have that.
yingyinNormal.zh: 普通芹菜。我已经写了。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey. Hey. I see you guys already met?
yingyinNormal.zh: 嗨。嗨，你们已经认识了？

yingyinNormal.en: But it already is your interest or hobby.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但它已经是你的兴趣爱好了。

yingyinNormal.en: Rebecca, Suzy and Emily are already here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瑞贝卡，苏西和艾米丽都已经到了。

yingyinNormal.en: When will she be ready? She already is.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她什么时候能准备好？她已经准备好了。

yingyinNormal.en: Rebecca, Suzy and Emily are already here.
yingyinNormal.zh: 瑞贝卡，苏西和艾米丽已经在这里了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, well, then you already have a retailer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 噢，好吧，那说明你已经有代理商了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, god, she's told you that already, didn't she?
yingyinNormal.zh: 天哪，她已经这么说了对吧？

yingyinNormal.en: Eli. Hi. Hi. You two are meeting already?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你来啦，伊莱。你们好，你俩已经谈过了吗？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Just 25 per cent of the country's land is suitable for crop-growing, most of which is <highlight>already</highlight> occupied by arable fields.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 该国仅有 25% 的土地适合种植农作物，而其中大部分已被耕地占用。

examination_example.sentence: In many parts of the world renewable energy is <highlight>already</highlight> a principal energy source.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在世界的许多地方，可再生能源已成为一种主要能源。

examination_example.sentence: "It's <highlight>already</highlight> a huge problem from a public expenditure perspective for the whole country," he says.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他说：“从公共支出的角度看，这对整个国家来说已经是一个巨大的难题。”

word_usage.usage:
already表示“已经”，通常用于肯定句，不用于否定句或疑问句（此时要用yet）。如：
He has already read the book.
他已经读过这本书。
He hasn't yet read this book.
他还没有读过这本书。

examination_example.sentence: I have <highlight>already</highlight> pointed out that people repeat ideas to signal they are part of the same social group.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我已经指出，人们重复想法是为了表明他们是同一个社会群体的一部分。

examination_example.sentence: By purchasing and consuming these types of products, have I <highlight>already</highlight> done some kind of harm to my family or the planet?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 通过购买和消费这些类型的产品，我是否已经对我的家庭或地球造成了某种伤害？

examination_example.sentence: It reduces our curiosity by showing us exactly what we <highlight>already</highlight> want and think, based on our profiles and preferences.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 基于我们的个人资料和偏好，它通过向我们展示我们已经想要和想的东西来减少我们的好奇心。
